# Easyplot toolbox
EasyplotPy is a software being developed by the research group headed by professor Wanderlei Malaquias Pereira Junior in Faculty of Engineering at Federal University of CatalÃ£o (UFCAT). EasyplotPy algorithm provide an easy workflow to assemble charts and save figures. The framework was developed in Python language.

